Head mover
A mover in the employ of the Silver Mustang Casino oversaw the delivery of a brand-new gym set to the home of Dougie and Janey-E Jones. He knocked on the front door to ask Janey-E where she wanted the set installed; stunned, she said the backyard would do. The mover pointed out that he had brought a new car for the family as well, courtesy of Rodney and Bradley Mitchum.
